object.script:
getN = input.getNumber setN = output.setNumber getB = input.getBool setB = output.setBool propN = property.getNumber
sin = math.sin cos = math.cos tan = math.tan atan = math.atan pi=math.pi
Radar_X=0 Radar_Y=0
Y_clamp=0 Ele_fin=0 x=1 y=1
TGT_angle=0
mode=0 level_flight=false
TGT_dist=0 Velocty=0 function onTick()
--Sensor value Alt=getN(1) Ele_tilt=getN(2) Compass=getN(3)
--GPS value GPSx=getN(4) GPSy=getN(5) D_GPSx=getN(6) D_GPSy=getN(7)
--Target position deta SetX=getN(8) SetY=getN(9) R_Dist=getN(10) R_Azi=getN(11) R_Ele=getN(12)
--get bool Launch_signal=getB(1) Phase1=getB(2) Phase2=getB(3) Radar_detect=getB(4)
--Radar position if Radar_detect then Radar_X=R_Dist*cos(((1+Compass%1)%1*360+R_Azi*(-360)+90)%360/180*pi)+GPSx Radar_Y=R_Dist*sin(((1+Compass%1)%1*360+R_Azi*(-360)+90)%360/180*pi)+GPSy else Radar_X=0 Radar_Y=0 end
--target relative position and Yaw clamp, Elevation fin
REcoef=propN('Radar Elevation coefficient')
--Y_clamp1=propN('Yaw clamp') Y_clamp1=(propN('Yaw clamp')-1)/(244-105)*Velocty+1-(propN('Yaw clamp')-1)/(244-105)*105
DSD=propN('Descent start distance[m]')
if Phase2 and not Radar_detect then Y_clamp=Y_clamp1 Ele_fin=0 x=SetX-GPSx y=SetY-GPSy mode=1 level_flight=true elseif Phase2 and Radar_detect then Y_clamp=1 x=Radar_X-GPSx y=Radar_Y-GPSy TGT_dist=(x^2+y^2)^(1/2) if TGT_dist<DSD then Ele_fin=0.14+(R_Ele)*REcoef level_flight=false mode=3 else Ele_fin=0 level_flight=true mode=2 end
elseif Phase1 then Y_clamp=Y_clamp1 Ele_fin=0 x=GPSx-D_GPSx y=GPSy-D_GPSy mode=0 level_flight=true end
TGT_angle=(atan(y,x)/pi*180+360)%360
--Velocity vector data Delta_x=GPSx-D_GPSx Delta_y=GPSy-D_GPSy
V_angle=(atan(Delta_y,Delta_x)/pi*180+360)%360 --0 to 360 deg, East=0, North=90
DeltaDist=(Delta_x^2+Delta_y^2)^(1/2) --m/tick Velocty=DeltaDist*60 --m/s
--target relative angle and Yaw fin Relative_angle=(V_angle-TGT_angle+180)%360-180
DSP=propN('DSP [deg]') Exp=propN('Exponent')
Yaw_fin=(Relative_angle/DSP)^Exp Yaw_fin=math.max(math.min(Y_clamp,Yaw_fin),-Y_clamp)
setN(1,Alt) setN(2,Ele_tilt) setN(3,Compass) setN(4,GPSx) setN(5,GPSy) setN(6,D_GPSx) setN(7,D_GPSy) setN(8,SetX) setN(9,SetY) setN(10,R_Dist) setN(11,R_Azi) setN(12,R_Ele) setN(20,Ele_fin) setN(21,Yaw_fin)
Ele_fin_back=getN(13) setN(22,Ele_fin_back)
setN(23,TGT_dist)
setN(24,Velocty)
setN(32,mode)
setB(1,Launch_signal) setB(2,Phase1) setB(3,Phase2) setB(4,Radar_detect) setB(5,level_flight)
end
